    <!-- DFP Lazy Loading Script -->
    <script type="text/javascript">
     function buildSlots() {
		__tcfapi('getTCData', 2, function (tcData, success) {
			if (success && (tcData.eventStatus === "tcloaded" || tcData.eventStatus === "useractioncomplete")) {
				let dfp_slots = document.querySelectorAll(".dfp-uninitialized");
				if (dfp_slots.length > 0) {
					dfp_slots.forEach(function (dfp_slot) {
						buildSlot(dfp_slot);
					});
				}
				refreshSlots();
			} else {
				slots = [];
			}
		});
	}

	function buildSlot(elem) {
		let id = elem.dataset.id;
		let dfp_id = elem.dataset.dfp_id + id;
		let sizes = elem.dataset.sizes;
		let map = window['map_' + elem.dataset.map];

		sizes = sizes.replace(/'/g, "\"");
		let size_array = JSON.parse(sizes);

		if ( typeof(map) !== 'undefined') {
			googletag.cmd.push(function() {
				slots.push(googletag.defineSlot(dfp_id, size_array, 'div-'+id).defineSizeMapping(map).addService(googletag.pubads()));
				googletag.display('div-'+id);
			});
		} else {
			googletag.cmd.push(function() {
				slots.push(googletag.defineSlot(dfp_id, size_array, 'div-'+id).addService(googletag.pubads()));
				googletag.display('div-'+id);
			});
		}

		document.getElementById('rm-adslot-' + id).classList.remove('dfp-uninitialized');
	}

	// add eventlisteners to refresh slots from slots objects.
	window.addEventListener('newPage', function(e){ buildSlots(); }, false );
    </script>
    <!-- END DFP Lazy Loading Script -->
    <script type="text/javascript">
     (function (window, document, undefined) {
		'use strict';
		const config = { rootMargin: '300px 0px', threshold: 0.01 };

		let observer;
		let cg_tags = window.document.querySelectorAll('.cg-tag-lazy');

		let onIntersection = function onIntersetion(entries) {
			entries.forEach(function(entry) {
				if (entry.intersectionRatio > 0) {
					// Stop watching and load the ad
					observer.unobserve(entry.target);
					// call our method: lazyLoadAd
					lazyLoadAd(entry.target);
				}
			});
		}

		let addNewAdsToObserver = function addNewAdsToObserver() {
			console.log('lazy loading content-garden: Collect all slots after new page event.');
			cg_tags = window.document.querySelectorAll('.cg-tag-lazy');
			if(cg_tags.length > 0) {
				cg_tags.forEach(function(cg_tag) {
					lazyLoadAd(cg_tag);
				});
			}
		};

		// Create script node and add it to content garden ad position.
		let lazyLoadAd = function lazyLoadAds(element) {

			let scriptTag = document.createElement('script');
			let cgId = element.dataset.id;

			scriptTag.src = 'https://cdn.content-garden.com/tag.js?wp_id=' + cgId;
			scriptTag.className = 'cg-tag';
			scriptTag.type = 'text/javascript';

			element.classList.remove('cg-tag-lazy');
			element.appendChild(scriptTag);
		}

		// Load visible ads directly.
		window.addEventListener('newPage', addNewAdsToObserver );

		// If we don't have support for intersection observer, load the ads immediately
		if (!('IntersectionObserver' in window)) {
			Array.from(cg_tags).forEach(function(lazy_ad){
				lazyLoadAd(cg_tags);
			});
		} else {
			// It is supported, load the ads by calling our method: onIntersection
			observer = new IntersectionObserver(onIntersection, config);
			cg_tags.forEach(function(cg_tags){
				observer.observe(cg_tags);
			});
		};
	})(window, document);
    </script>
